patthana12.6:1.1_0: Nahetuṁ nadassanena pahātabbaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ. Sabbattha nava.)
patthana12.6:2.1_0: Nahetuṁ nanadassanena pahātabbaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ. Sabbattha nava. Vipākaṁ natthi.)
patthana12.6:8.1_0: Nahetuṁ naaniyataṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe…. (Saṅkhittaṁ. Sabbattha nava. Vipākaṁ natthi.)
patthana12.6:10.1_0: Nahetuṁ nasaraṇaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nahetu nasaraṇo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Sabbattha nava.)
patthana12.6:11.1_0: Nahetuṁ naaraṇaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nahetu naaraṇo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana12.6:11.1_1: Nahetuṁ naaraṇaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nanahetu naaraṇo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana12.6:11.1_2: Nahetuṁ naaraṇaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nahetu naaraṇo ca nanahetu naaraṇo ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā.
patthana12.6:12.1_0: Nanahetuṁ naaraṇaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nanahetu naaraṇo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana12.6:12.1_1: Nanahetuṁ naaraṇaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nahetu naaraṇo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana12.6:12.1_2: Nanahetuṁ naaraṇaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nahetu naaraṇo ca nanahetu naaraṇo ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā.
patthana12.6:13.1_0: Nahetuṁ naaraṇañca nanahetuṁ naaraṇañca dhammaṁ paṭicca nahetu naaraṇo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana12.6:13.1_1: Nahetuṁ naaraṇañca nanahetuṁ naaraṇañca dhammaṁ paṭicca nanahetu naaraṇo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana12.6:13.1_2: Nahetuṁ naaraṇañca nanahetuṁ naaraṇañca dhammaṁ paṭicca nahetu naaraṇo ca nanahetu naaraṇo ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā.
